        <updateDate>2003-08-04T22:43:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Family Fairness in Taxing Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the child care credit to: (1) revise refundability criteria; (2) accelerate the increase to a $1,000 credit; and (3) increase a qualifying child's age to 19 years old.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
